          <td colspan="2" valign="top" class="titulo2">A Reading of Things (1988) <span class="texto2">an essay by <a href="../../issue9/jorge_edwards/bio.php" class="link3">Jorge Edwards</a><br>Translated from the Spanish by <a href="http://interlitq.org/staff/peter_robertson/bio.php" class="link3">Peter Robertson</a></span></td>
